parameters: It's been a few days since then...
I wonder if Uncle gets lonely...
He wasn't such a bad person after all...
...Maybe I should go visit him once in a while.

\N<Hinata Aki> ...Uncle? I came because I had some free
time...?

\N<Hinata Aki> You're too happy~ I just happened to be
passing by, so I thought I'd show my face.

\N<Sayama> I see, I see!! It's a dirty place, but please
make yourself at home and relax.
\N<Hinata Aki> Yeah, I'm here to intrude~

\N<Hinata Aki> Ah~ You were looking at your phone again
today.

\N<Sayama> Ah... Whenever I have free time, I end up looking
at it.

\N<Sayama> This photo was taken during the sports
festival... and this photo...
<Hinata Aki> Let me see~ Show me~

\N<Sayama> Oh, by the way, let me take a picture of you too,
sis.

\N<Sayama> Because I feel like it might fill the loneliness
a bit.

\N<Sayama> Is it no good...? It's probably no good, right...
I mean, who would trust a request from a suspicious old man
like me...

\N<Hinata Aki> Hmm... Hmm... Well... If it's just one photo?
I guess it's fine...
\N<Sayama> Really!?... Then let's do it right away!
\N<Hinata Aki> Eh? Ah! All of a sudden...!

\N<Hinata Aki> I-I'll work part-time to compensate! I'll
definitely compensate!
\N<Hinata Aki> If there's anything I can do, I'll do it!
\N<Hinata Aki> Yeah... What do you want me to say?
\N<Hinata Aki> If that's okay with you...
\N<Hinata Aki> Hmm... It feels a bit embarrassing...

\N<Sayama> It's been a while since I've felt the warmth of
another person...

\N<Hinata Aki> ...Is that so... Well, I guess that's a
relief?
Breathing... rough... Does that mean you're happy, old man?
\N<Sayama> Ah... I'm glad to be alive...

\N<Sayama> Ugh... I don't have anything to distract myself
when I'm alone anymore...
Ah... your hand on my chest...

It must be really lonely... I'll endure it for a little
while...
Hasn't my chest been touched?... But it's hard to say...
I was hugged continuously until the uncle was satisfied.
Being alone in that tent is probably lonely after all.

My phone... I broke it, so... I'll go see your face during
summer vacation, at least...
